snippet.textDisplay:
I live in a city affected by the coronavirus, and it's been under lockdown since the Chinese New Year (January 25). My neighborhood is barricaded, and residents aren't allowed to go out.

One afternoon my wife developed a cough. She said her throat hurt, but her temperature was normal. An hour later, she nervously showed me the thermometer: her temperature was 37.4 Celsius (99.3 Fahrenheit).

I said she was fine and we shouldn't worry. By evening, her temperature had risen to 38.5 Celsius (101.3 Fahrenheit). I grew a little nervous too, as her rising temperature was a symptom of the coronavirus.

We dared not go to the hospital fearing we'd be placed in isolation. The drug store had already closed for the night. We didn't know what to do as we're seniors (I'm 80 years old and she's 76).

I began practicing Falun Dafa in 1996. I told my wife, “Only Master Li can save you. Keep saying, ‘Falun Dafa is good’ and ‘Truthfulness-Compassion-Forbearance is good.’”

When she said she repeated them, I said, “But you weren't sincere. When I told you about the persecution, you said some disrespectful things about Master and Dafa.

“On New Year's Day I told the family about the epidemic. But you've all been misled by the Chinese Communist Party’s (CCP) propaganda. You didn't take what I said seriously.

“You keep singing songs that praise the CCP and watching shows on TV that glorify the Party. When you say the phrases, you're not sincere. How can Master save you?”

I read her some of Master’s poems in Hong Yin Volume III. I said, “Our entire family has benefited from my practice, but you all continue to disrespect Falun Dafa. We have Master’s portrait displayed in our home. Please apologize and ask Master to save you.”

My wife's attitude changed. She stood in front of Master's portrait and very seriously said, “Falun Dafa is good. Truthfulness-Compassion-Forbearance is good.”

After she went to bed at 10 p.m. she began to sweat. I got up at 3 a.m. and began to do the Dafa exercises as usual. My wife's temperature dropped to 37.7 Celsius (99.8 Fahrenheit). By 1 p.m., her temperature was normal. She stopped coughing and her throat no longer hurt. Within 20 hours of the first symptom, she had fully recovered.

Out of gratitude and respect, my wife now lights incense in front of Master’s portrait every day. Her attitude about Falun Dafa has completely changed. We are both grateful to Master.

snippet.textDisplay:
Cher monsieur 武田
徳多き賢人さま。私、おじさまの言ってることに賛成だわ。幸せはお金では買えない。教育は利己ではなく利他のためにある。シンプルだけど難しい言葉。なぜって、そんなこと私、学校の先生から聞いた覚えがないわ。あの人たちの言うことといったら、「今でしょ」とか「すき間時間」なんて実用的なことばっかり。まるで冷えきったコンクリートね。

私、今日素敵な子に会ったわ。そうね、名前は、、、「さわ」としておきましょう。さわわね、素直でさっぱりして明るい子。目はくりっとして、いたづらっ子みたいによく動くの。私はどちらかというと、スローで口下手な天然なの。だからさわの頭の回転にはついていけない気がするわ。ああ、仲良くなれるか心配だわ。

おじさま、私、この世で誰かと誰かが心を通い合わせるほど素敵なことってないと思うわ。今日わね、北杜夫の「むすめよ…」を読んで涙ぐんちゃった。そこにはお父さんが娘を想う気持ちが正直に綴られているの。私、お父さんやお母さんの視点で赤ちゃんの頃から今に至るまでの私を思い描いたわ。それは愛そのものだった。

なんだか書いていて恥ずかしいじゃないの。おじさま、私明日にはきっとこのコメントを削除してしまうわ。決してそれまでには読まないでね。

さようなら
Au revoir
"Piento luego existo"
